flowchart TD
    A[Identify Hiring Need] --> B[Job Analysis and Job Description]
    B --> C[Obtain Approvals]
    C --> D[Post Job Opening]
    D --> E[Receive and Review Applications]
    E --> F[Conduct Initial Interviews]
    F --> G[Assessment and Testing]
    G --> H[Conduct Final Interviews]
    H --> I[Perform Reference Checks]
    I --> J[Make Job Offer]
    J --> K[Onboarding]
    K --> L[Feedback and Continuous Improvement]
